    <briefdescription>
<para>Seeds the database from SQL files. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The seeder runs at application startup when the database is empty. Splits the SQL into batches and applies them inside transactions to avoid large single-statement execution. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
